em>","Vera Control Ltd. offers smart home controllers with good device and software compatibility. Vera&#39;s features are not as extensive the higher ranked products in our lineup, but the home automation system still has much to offer with robust technical support and a strong community of users around the globe.","Vera&#39;s best feature is its support of remote access. The MiOS software of this smart home system can connect with any web browser or Android and iOS smartphone apps, which have an intuitive interface to help you achieve maximum control and energy efficiency while you&#39;re away from home. Vera allows you to program the smart house system to react to the sunrise, the sunset, the doorbell and much more.","The system can even be programmed with random events to deter thieves while you&#39;re on vacation. Vera is compatible with many different security system components such as cameras and motion detectors. Like many of the less expensive home automation systems, Vera is not compatible with home theater systems. Vera also does not support voice control technology.","Vera boasts peripheral compatibility with Wi-Fi, Insteon, X10, ZigBee and Z-Wave home control technologies. These control technologies are available on a variety of devices such as light bulbs, smoke detectors, door sensors and much more. This smart home system works with most smart thermostats and HVAC systems to help you increase heating and cooling efficiency in your home.","Vera gives you the choice between four native hardware controllers: VeraEdge, Vera3, VeraLite and the VeraLite G. The VeraEdge and Vera3 are designed for more advanced home automation systems. Similarly, the VeraLite series performs the same functions in a more simplified capacity, but its wireless Z-Wave range is smaller.","The technical support for this product is outstanding. You can contact Vera support by email, telephone and live chat if you want a direct response to your question. If you prefer to troubleshoot the system on your own, Vera has extensive options available such as a user manual, FAQs, a lively forum and tutorials. Vera does not require professional installation, which gives it an advantage over higher ranked systems in our review."]},"id":"e29d20e5-610a-4163-9639-6fd14c3308ba","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"cc3be067-515b-434f-8d14-ae5dbf7d11f2","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Vera is designed to work for you, regardless of whether you are a beginner or a home automation guru. Vera&#39;s strong points are its excellent technical support and its helpful remote access function. Vera is a great option for a low-budget, intelligent home system."]},"id":"a4c64962-971c-4f95-aefd-6552a5fad824","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_59238","url":"/vera-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-03-27T14:00:13Z","datePublished":"2014-03-27T14:00:13Z","name":"Vera","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Home Automation Systems here.","review":{"rating":91,"verdict":"Vera has one of the best remote access functions in our review and is well suited for both beginners and advanced users.","pros":["Only one other product in our review even comes close to the quality of Vera&#039;s outstanding technical support."],"cons":["This automation system is not compatible with home theater systems."]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 abou